      <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl mb-4">The situation before we started</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-500 leading-relaxed mb-5">The contractor had been in the local market for years with a solid reputation, but did not appear on Google when someone searched for their service in the area. They had not invested in digital advertising because they were not sure it would work for their type of business.</p>
      <p class="text-gray-500 leading-relaxed mb-8">The main concern was: spending money on ads without knowing whether they would reach real customers. The first step was reviewing their digital foundation before activating any advertising.</p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl mb-4">What we did</h2>
      <ul class="checklist mb-8">
        <li><strong>Digital presence audit</strong> — we reviewed their GBP, existing web presence, local keywords, and competitors to establish the starting point.</li>
        <li><strong><a href="/en/services/google-business-profile-treasure-coast/" style="color:var(--primary)">Google Business Profile</a> optimization</strong> — professional photos, correct categories, review responses, and the first local posts.</li>
        <li><strong>Conversion-focused <a href="/en/services/web-design-treasure-coast/" style="color:var(--primary)">landing page</a></strong> — a dedicated page with a clear offer, real job photos, a quote request form, and a prominent WhatsApp button.</li>
        <li><strong><a href="/en/services/google-ads-treasure-coast/" style="color:var(--primary)">Google Ads</a> campaign</strong> — ads targeted by city and service type, with controlled budget and conversion tracking from day one.</li>
        <li>Monthly reports showing clicks, calls, and quote requests received.</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl mb-4">Results</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-500 leading-relaxed mb-6">The first quote requests came in during the first week after the ads went live. Detailed metrics are pending confirmation with the client.</p>

